; AutoCAD Script File - Batch Plot All Layouts
; Plots all layouts to PDF with standard settings

; Set plotting preferences
BACKGROUNDPLOT 0
FILEDIA 0

; Plot each layout (script will repeat for each layout)
; This is a template - actual implementation would need layout names

; Set plot device to PDF
-PLOT _Y _L _A _F _N _N _A _N _N _N _C _Y _N _N _N _Y

; Alternative: Export all layouts to PDF
-EXPORTPDF _ALL _Y

; Turn file dialog back on
FILEDIA 1

QSAVE